---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import styles from "./what_we_do.module.css";
---

<BaseLayout title="Bramel offering | Boutique investment bank" currentPage="/what_we_do">
  <main class={styles.page}>
    <div class={styles.content}>
      <h1 class={styles.heading}>What we do</h1>
      <h2 class={styles.industriesHeading}>Industries</h2>

      <div class={styles.leftBody}>
        <p class={styles.text}>
          Bramel's multi-disciplinary skillset and its considerable experience
          enables a broad-range of service offerings for clients, partners and
          principals.
        </p>

        <p class={styles.text}>
          Having worked on a multitude of corporate transactions, capital
          raising and investment opportunities, Bramel's investment banking
          capabilities are broad and include:
        </p>

        <ul class={styles.bulletList}>
          <li class={styles.bulletItem}>Mergers &amp; acquisitions</li>
          <li class={styles.bulletItem}>Management and leveraged buyouts</li>
          <li class={styles.bulletItem}>Listings and delistings</li>
          <li class={styles.bulletItem}>Capital raising, including equity and debt funding</li>
          <li class={styles.bulletItem}>Special opportunity transactions</li>
        </ul>

        <p class={styles.text}>
          Additionally, Bramel supports company shareholders and
          management teams with strategic input into management of assets
          and value realisation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class={styles.rightBody}>
        <p class={styles.industriesIntro}>
          Bramel's team has experience in most industries, including:
        </p>

        <ul class={styles.industryList}>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Industrial (including manufacturing)</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Real estate</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Mining (including oil &amp; gas)</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Technology (including fintech)</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Financial services</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Transport &amp; logistics</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Consumer goods (retail and wholesale)</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Construction</li>
          <li class={styles.industryItem}>Energy (including renewable)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
